metadata.name: Home is Belonging
metadata.description:
"Home is Belonging" 

Is a representation of the concept that home is not just a physical space, but a collection of people, memories, and experiences which come together to create a sense of belonging and comfort. This pieces invites everyone to reflect on what "home" means to them personally, and the things that one had to through in life to create a space that truly embodies their own sense of belonging. 

This is an AI assisted piece.
